### Test Helper System (Updated)

### 1. Check Firebase Status (Debug)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/helper/firebase-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Create helper request
POST http://localhost:3001/api/helper/request
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requesterId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "requesterName": "Test User",
  "helperIds": ["HELPER_ID_1", "HELPER_ID_2"]
}

### 3. Respond to helper request
POST http://localhost:3001/api/helper/respond
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "REQUEST_ID_HERE",
  "helperId": "HELPER_ID_HERE",
  "response": "accepted"
}

### 4. Respond to helper request (decline)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/helper/respond
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "REQUEST_ID_HERE",
  "helperId": "HELPER_ID_HERE",
  "response": "declined"
}

### 5. Get my helper requests (as helper)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/helper/my-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Get my requests as requester
GET http://localhost:3001/api/helper/my-requests-as-requester
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Get all users (to see helper status)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
